Boutique room | Hotel | Varberg Stadshotell & Asia Spa
All the 66 boutique rooms have their own individual style and furnishings, designed with a modern, yet totally unique flair.  How about sleeping in a crisp Winter Wonderland, an African safari lounge or an urban design metropolis. In this part of our hotel, you will discover innovative approaches and special design features such as circular beds and a bespoke bathtub in the middle of the room.
Boutique Garden in beige/champagne
Three magnificent rooms with nostalgic charm from the colonial era. A copper tub in the middle of the room and a grand four-poster bed.
