Hot springs
19 JUNE–21 AUGUST
POOL & SAUNA
Lovely summer package with four overnight stays and half a day access to Asia Spa. Bring the whole family and celebrate your holiday with us in Varberg!
We have several different kinds of saunas for you to try and a tropical rainforest for that all-important cool-down in between or afterwards. Enjoy a good soak in the Japanese hot springs, relax and rest your eyes on the horizon and Varberg Fortress, before heading into the vitality pool for a salubrious massage in the warm water measuring 30 degrees C.
Here you can explore and enjoy several different kinds of saunas. Eucalyptus soothes stiff joints in the steam room and the 45 degrees C heat of the salt sauna gently envelops your entire body. Try out the low-temperature sauna or cool down every now and then in our tropical rainforest shower. Right at the heart of our sauna oasis, you can cool down with a refreshing plunge in the cold tub.
The foot basins at Asia Spa overlook the Japanese hot springs and the coastline outside, perfect for indulging your feet and relaxing your mind. Pour a scoop of salt into the water, lean back and give your feet a good soak for at least 10 minutes.
