Michael’s signature ladder flow class! This class is a strong, fun and energizing asana practice. Let the breath and the music guide you as you learn short sequences one after the other, linking them together throughout the practice to create one long flow that we can move, breathe and feel together! This is a powerful practice of learning, forgetting, feeling and flowing.
