Sinking into stillness
Your aura is the energy you share with the world. In this kundalini meditation and mantra class you will do breathwork and chants that help you radiate positive energy so that you can feel calm, supported and bright.
During this class you’ll be guided through a variety of breath practices (pranayama) to help access, free-up, unburden, and ground the body before moving into a restorative yoga sequence. Restorative yoga offers you the opportunity to land into the cushioned support of bolsters, blankets and props, helping the body to surrender into more therapeutic positions to foster an evolved state of restoration and repair for the body, mind and spirit.
A dynamic vinyasa class where we will use the Sun Salutations as a framework to increase the flow of prana in our bodies while opening up our heart space and exploring the Anahata chakra (the heart chakra). It will be meditation in motion. This session is open to all levels.
